room_title: Escape room "Time Machine" by Not Another Escape Room in Pomona
room_description: Rumor has it that when Calvin J. Lloyd died he left his nephew a time machine. Now, the nephew has gone missing and his family believes that he may be trapped somewhere in time. You have been hired as a group of investigators to look into this missing persons case to see if you can find the nephew and prove once and for all if time travel is possible.
